"", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASZaX8n5g", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 26, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8589214, "raw_content": "Major blow to the \u201cout of Africa theory\u201d as fossils of hominids in Europe are discovered which date roughly back to the same time as hominid fossils in Africa. \n\n[Takes us closer to the tower of Babel where it is written that the Lord God confused the languages of men so as to forcibly disperse them throughout the world as a consequence for their displayed arrogance (Gen. 11) and if such an event did take place, then it would be expected that people had settled in both Europe and Africa roughly around the same time and were not necessarily descended from one another]\n\nhttps://chicagopixels.net/", "author": "ContendersEdge", "created": 1777478596946, "profile_picture": "OTUZVRkFHNZn", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "CommanderOfCheese", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Major blow to the \u201cout of Africa theory\u201d as fossils of hominids in Europe are discovered which date roughly back to the same time as hominid fossils in Africa. \n", "last_comment_created": 1777482965949, "content": "<p>Major blow to the \u201cout of Africa theory\u201d as fossils of hominids in Europe are discovered which date roughly back to the same time as hominid fossils in Africa.</p>\n<p>[Takes us closer to the tower of Babel where it is written that the Lord God confused the languages of men so as to forcibly disperse them throughout the world as a consequence for their displayed arrogance (Gen. 11) and if such an event did take place, then it would be expected that people had settled in both Europe and Africa roughly around the same time and were not necessarily descended from one another]</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://chicagopixels.net/\" target=\"_blank\">https://chicagopixels.net/</a></p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 6, "score_up": 26, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2049178517145838051", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASZaW1V6B", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 71, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8588663, "raw_content": "", "author": "blue5707", "created": 1777457755353, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Rusty520", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASZaW1V6B.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/mikebenzcyber/status/2049178517145838051?s=46", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "\u2026not \u201ctoo smart\u201d after all\u2026", "last_comment_created": 1777470522396, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 2, "score_up": 71, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"twitter": {"quotedTweet": {"quotedTweet": false, "images": [{"width": 1080, "heightRatio": 125, "url": "https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HG_36FHWYAAtw6v.jpg", "height": 1350}, {"width": 1080, "heightRatio": 125, "url": "https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HG_36FXXgAA1nqM.jpg", "height": 135